snippet.textDisplay: The tapes tell you all you need to know. Amber in her own voice telling you how she assaults him, how she can’t promise she won’t get physical again and how she gets so mad she loses it. She belittles him and tells him to jerk off his security guard. She complains he runs away from her every time she starts a fight, does that sound like a woman who was in fear for her life?
